page_id: S4-LNX-01
title: Choose AreaMatrix Repository
description: Select a local folder for your AreaMatrix repository. Network drives and third-party sync folders may behave differently across Linux distributions.
field: Repository folder
primary_actions:
  - Browse...
  - Use default: ~/AreaMatrix
  - Continue
  - Cancel
states:
  checking: Checking folder...
  initialized: Existing AreaMatrix repository
  empty: Empty folder
  non_empty: Non-empty folder
  permission_denied: Permission denied
  network_or_removable: Network or removable path detected
routes:
  initialized: S4-LNX-02
  empty: S4-X-04
  non_empty: S4-X-05
  high_risk: S4-LNX-03
safety:
  - The page calls validate_repo_path through LinuxRepositoryCoreBridge.
  - The page does not create folders.
  - The page does not initialize or adopt repositories before confirmation.
  - The page does not suggest sudo or chmod.
